    "description": "<p>A world-leading tannery under the LVMH group that supplies high quality exotic leather to major international fashion houses and customers globally.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Drawing on nearly 70 years of industry experience, Heng Long has transformed a traditional craft into the fine art of tanning and leather finishing.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Heng Long's accumulated expertise and extensive knowledge in the intricacies of the reptile skin tanning industry, coupled with its commitment to research and development, are fundamental to the success of the Company. Its modern production facility in Singapore employs advanced technology to produce the best quality leather to meet the exacting demands of its international customers.</p>",
